@startuml sequence_diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #F6F8FA
skinparam participantBorderColor #0969DA
skinparam participantFontColor #1F2328
skinparam arrowColor #57606A
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8C5
skinparam noteBorderColor #E3B341
skinparam noteFontColor #1F2328
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

title 四层权限管道 - 时序图 (Sequence Diagram)\n三种典型决策路径

actor "调用方" as Caller #F6F8FA
participant "PermissionPipeline" as PP #F6F8FA
participant "Layer1\nRuleMatcher" as L1 #DDF4FF
participant "Layer2\nBashClassifier" as L2 #FFF8C5
participant "Layer3\nTranscriptClassifier" as L3 #FBEFFF
participant "Layer4\nModelSafety" as L4 #FFEFF0

== 场景 A: 第一层快速命中 (Read/Grep 等只读操作) ==

Caller -> PP : check(ToolCall, history)
activate PP

PP -> L1 : decide(tool_call, history)
activate L1
note right of L1
  fnmatch 通配符匹配
  deny 优先于 allow
end note
L1 --> PP : **ALLOW** (命中允许规则)
deactivate L1

PP --> Caller : PipelineResult(ALLOW, 0.5ms)
deactivate PP

note over Caller, L1
  管道在第一层终止，不再执行后续层
end note

== 场景 B: 第二层拦截危险操作 (force push / rm -rf 等) ==

Caller -> PP : check(ToolCall, history)
activate PP

PP -> L1 : decide()
activate L1
L1 --> PP : PASS (未匹配任何规则)
deactivate L1

note over PP : PASS → 继续下一层

PP -> L2 : decide()
activate L2
note right of L2
  仅检查 Bash 工具
  22+ 预编译正则模式
end note
L2 --> PP : **DENY** (检测到危险模式)
deactivate L2

PP --> Caller : PipelineResult(DENY, 3ms)
deactivate PP

note over Caller, L2
  管道在第二层终止，第三/四层不执行
end note

== 场景 C: 四层全部传递，模型最终判定 ==

Caller -> PP : check(ToolCall, history)
activate PP

PP -> L1 : decide()
L1 --> PP : PASS

PP -> L2 : decide()
L2 --> PP : PASS

PP -> L3 : decide()
activate L3
note right of L3
  检查安全/危险信号
  只读操作直接 ALLOW
  非只读但无明确信号 → PASS
end note
L3 --> PP : PASS (上下文信息不足)
deactivate L3

PP -> L4 : decide()
activate L4
note right of L4
  模拟 LLM API 调用 (50~200ms)
  计算风险评分:
    命令关键字 +0.3
    危险目标路径 +0.25
    强制标志 +0.2
    危险上下文 +0.15
    score >= 0.5 → DENY
    score < 0.5 → ALLOW
end note
L4 --> PP : **ALLOW** (score=0.25)
deactivate L4

PP --> Caller : PipelineResult(ALLOW, 120ms)
deactivate PP

note over Caller, L4
  **若四层均 PASS → 默认 DENY (安全优先原则)**
end note

legend right
  |= 图例 |= 说明 |
  | <color:#0969DA>━━▶</color> | 实线箭头 = 请求/调用 |
  | <color:#1A7F37>━━◀</color> | 绿色返回 = ALLOW |
  | <color:#CF222E>━━◀</color> | 红色返回 = DENY |
  | <color:#BF8700>━━◀</color> | 黄色返回 = PASS (传递到下一层) |
  |= 参与者颜色 |= 层级 |
  | <color:#0969DA>■</color> Layer1 | RuleMatcher (规则匹配, <1ms) |
  | <color:#BF8700>■</color> Layer2 | BashClassifier (危险命令检测, ~1ms) |
  | <color:#8250DF>■</color> Layer3 | TranscriptClassifier (上下文分析, ~5ms) |
  | <color:#CF222E>■</color> Layer4 | ModelSafety (模型安全分类, 50~200ms) |
  |= 决策语义 | |
  | ALLOW | 安全，允许执行，管道终止 |
  | DENY | 危险，拒绝执行，管道终止 |
  | PASS | 当前层无法判定，交给下一层 |
endlegend

@enduml
